{"tid":747404,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"HK Express 亂加「路牌」","createTime":"2018-07-18T10:51:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-22T07:02:12.000Z","uid":62085,"like":178,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":93,"replies":[{"pid":"e79e35c754bf4920295292b31f970b645074aad9","tid":747404,"uid":62085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T10:51:33.000Z","msg":"HK Express再陷公關災難！公民黨東區區議員鄭達鴻表示，近日收到北角區居民反映在炮台山一處路牌下，發現另有一個疑似路牌的物品，「嗰牌上面無任何公司標示，只有一個QR Code」，他仔細研究及追查，始發現涉及HK Express的宣傳活動有關。他指單在北角及炮台山就有最少有超過20塊相關宣傳路牌。本報正查詢路政署及HK Express回應。<br />\n<br />\n鄭達鴻稱，自己幾日前已於炮台山一個路牌下方發現該疑似路牌的物品，當時不以為意，直至近日有北角居民向他查詢相關路牌的出處，才發現是仿制品。鄭指有居民投訴部分宣傳路牌擺放的位置過低，會撞及路過行人的頭部；又指相關宣傳路牌引起居民恐慌，「點解無啦啦會有多一塊路牌喺度，（宣傳路牌）又完全無HK Express任何標誌，淨係有QR Code，你唔會期望一個街坊無啦啦喺街道掃QR Code，依家QR Code過錢都過到啦」，他批評HK Express此舉是不負責任行為，「你要搞宣傳活動唔緊要，但你至少要負責任俾番自己公司名落去宣傳品度。」 他將會向路政署及HK Express投訴。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHK Express回應指，對於相關活動之安排為公眾帶來不便，深表歉意，今天 (7月18日) 會暫停有關活動，現正移除已張貼之路牌，並由明晚 (7月19日) 起以其他方式繼續進行遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180718/58456747\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180718%2F58456747&d=wTiTSq3ToBVfcOFyxNleLl0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=c9e4a6ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180718%2F58456747&h=8ca5f3e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180718/58456747</a><br />\n<br />\n屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 宣傳都唔落自己公司Logo"},{"pid":"32af66b114a2014c15e98a50204b6aa001526931","tid":747404,"uid":62085,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T10:55:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f709aada7d4b4cd9a0c877af2a1e349bf55a51dd","tid":747404,"uid":34010,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T10:58:00.000Z","msg":"qrcode上腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcb726ad5bfffcc41c19a77650e0e6596f014226","tid":747404,"uid":62085,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T12:01:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f1409415d9cfc6658722bec1745183e5b496037","tid":747404,"uid":3241,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T12:47:57.000Z","msg":"上環星期一都出現一大把<br />\n1823送左佢一程"},{"pid":"b9f3605e4dd0c903a3d2c7b0062cce996d6b3593","tid":747404,"uid":24345,"like":79,"dislike":6,"score":73,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T12:50:28.000Z","msg":"郁啲就話公關災難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ada88ec44806236eea7d009f967720a7cd485e4","tid":747404,"uid":12001,"like":123,"dislike":1,"score":122,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T12:50:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/204953_94ee930eddfdb36ee3535ea59cfcabf2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F204953_94ee930eddfdb36ee3535ea59cfcabf2.png&h=2cbb3c39&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/205002_2befdf67308be12ff96820599b48588f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F205002_2befdf67308be12ff96820599b48588f.png&h=0cb64cf1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一朝早出門口見所有路牌都有嚇一嚇"},{"pid":"20d142bfc7ca186fe30d9583ae78f0bee577eead","tid":747404,"uid":64874,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T13:24:52.000Z","msg":"我係旺角花園街間唐記包點對出都有，原來係賣機票"},{"pid":"b3bab4037d16cd390dc86d50f12c35c9b13ae764","tid":747404,"uid