a39f51","tid":747404,"uid":7155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c950238c39f4e033677d05779625bfbb84dff420","tid":747404,"uid":51920,"like":5,"dislike":10,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T17:17:34.000Z","msg":"大陸公司: 犯法 阻街<br />\n外國公司: 有創意 香港人唔玩得 一定比師奶投訴 創意沙漠<br />\n<br />\nthis is 連登 logic"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T00:08:09.000Z","msg":"外國公司先唔會做啲咁on9 嘅野<br />\n叫做大少少嘅公司，做乜都要拎legal advice<br />\n呢啲活動邊有可能批 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a241e465553e24c803040898ada5a9a1ba0daf09","tid":747404,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T01:09:42.000Z","msg":"比班垃圾腦人睇"},{"pid":"7803091948104bf7f2fc834677901f78302cfc06","tid":747404,"uid":131245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e79e35c754bf4920295292b31f970b645074aad9","tid":747404,"uid":62085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T10:51:33.000Z","msg":"HK Express再陷公關災難！公民黨東區區議員鄭達鴻表示，近日收到北角區居民反映在炮台山一處路牌下，發現另有一個疑似路牌的物品，「嗰牌上面無任何公司標示，只有一個QR Code」，他仔細研究及追查，始發現涉及HK Express的宣傳活動有關。他指單在北角及炮台山就有最少有超過20塊相關宣傳路牌。本報正查詢路政署及HK Express回應。<br />\n<br />\n鄭達鴻稱，自己幾日前已於炮台山一個路牌下方發現該疑似路牌的物品，當時不以為意，直至近日有北角居民向他查詢相關路牌的出處，才發現是仿制品。鄭指有居民投訴部分宣傳路牌擺放的位置過低，會撞及路過行人的頭部；又指相關宣傳路牌引起居民恐慌，「點解無啦啦會有多一塊路牌喺度，（宣傳路牌）又完全無HK Express任何標誌，淨係有QR Code，你唔會期望一個街坊無啦啦喺街道掃QR Code，依家QR Code過錢都過到啦」，他批評HK Express此舉是不負責任行為，「你要搞宣傳活動唔緊要，但你至少要負責任俾番自己公司名落去宣傳品度。」 他將會向路政署及HK Express投訴。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHK Express回應指，對於相關活動之安排為公眾帶來不便，深表歉意，今天 (7月18日) 會暫停有關活動，現正移除已張貼之路牌，並由明晚 (7月19日) 起以其他方式繼續進行遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180718/58456747\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180718%2F58456747&d=wTiTSq3ToBVfcOFyxNleLl0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=c9e4a6ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180718%2F58456747&h=8ca5f3e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180718/58456747</a><br />\n<br />\n屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 宣傳都唔落自己公司Logo"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T01:11:39.000Z","msg":"依家咪有公司名囉，全世界都知佢又柒咗一穫，叻叻豬"},{"pid":"d2b2364c3be00bd57e8184310053ba9058ac05e6","tid":747404,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T01:12:30.000Z","msg":"最正係佢用foamboard，一打風落雨就爛"},{"pid":"02f8d35be0fd2c47983fc3f6e2cdfde08fecc286","tid":747404,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T01:19:51.000Z","msg":"跑台山天龍人區邊到有人行路，無野攞黎講"},{"pid":"881ac1a274e7ea425ac4e93d2d68f82a1c830633","tid":747404,"uid":36688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T01:27:47.000Z","msg":"咁到底係賣咩？新航綫？"},{"pid":"59d6e9ed740cfc4fc9f0db875cfd59698e03d53d","tid":747404,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"828ecac807b9294164363b0b799574a1cf5a3914","tid":747404,"uid":192935,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T13:37:00.000Z","msg":"marketing 可以炒左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T01:29:23.000Z","msg":"諗個team人比人小爆都似"},{"pid":"f398e7b75533adaa9d15b1a3e3f347a5d7cbbd0e","tid":747404,"uid":195169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T01:47:53.000Z","msg":"其實都幾慳皮喎<br />\nMKT偷雞唔到蝕渣米<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c4ae714fc9bf8d0acee23a8db788aedae93dd35","tid":747404,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T01:56:04.000Z","msg":"早排係廣華醫院果頭都見到有個路牌寫住&quot;讚岐烏冬&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"899417d849ad46fb8379017baf100c5bfd66e8bc","tid":747404,"uid":18477,"like":0,"di